Game Information:  

PC-version of a new project of the world famous series,
tells the story of ill-confrontation reasonable fighting robots.
Win the war, which became the beginning of the great confrontation!
War that erupted long before the Transformers came to Earth.
War for dominance in the Cybertron - home planet of mighty robots.
Two large-scale campaigns allow everyone to make a choice: to
protect Cybertron, speaking on the side of the noble Autobots, or
attempt to enslave the planet, fighting in the ranks
of the treacherous Decepticons.

Game Features:  

Fight on the side of the Autobots or Decepticons in two unique campaigns.
Create your own transformer and take part in immense online battles.
At any time, turn all the robot fighting in the vehicle.
Complete the campaign mode of playing together for three participants.
